<DOCID> 098663 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 15, 1994, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 1; Column 4; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
