<P>
 The Huntington Beach Conference and Visitors Bureau recently received the 1994 
Western Assn. of Convention and Visitors Bureaus award for outstanding 
achievement. 
</P>
<P>
 The city's tourist bureau received the recognition for its "Watercolors of the 
Coast" brochure promotion. 
</P>
