<TEXT>
<P>
 Faylane Elementary School will hold three parenting-skills workshops starting 
today, a school district spokesman said. 
</P>
<P>
 The free seminars will be held at 7 p.m. on consecutive Tuesdays in the 
multipurpose room of the school, at 11731 Morrie Lane, Garden Grove.They are 
open to Faylane and Gilbert Elementary School parents, said Alan Trudell, 
spokesman for the Garden Grove Unified School District. 
