<TEXT>
<P>
 Cafe shooting -- An article Sunday about a shooting at a Westminster coffee 
shop inaccurately recounted an incident last April at a nearby cafe, Pho Tien 
Canh. 
</P>
<P>
 In the April incident, an off-duty security guard shot two men -- one fatally 
-- in self-defense. 
</P>
